    <div class="section-body">
    <!-- COMPUTE: build one <svg width="100%" height="230" viewBox="0 0 1000 230"> with TWO
         lines sharing one coordinate mapping:
           x-axis: spans [earliest trajektorie.history[].date_de .. the later of
           trajektorie.target_date_de / trajektorie.stretch_date_de], parsed as dd.mm.yyyy
           and mapped linearly onto x = 0..1000 (only the _de fields exist — parse those,
           never expect a raw ISO date alongside them).
           y-axis: 0% at y=200 (baseline, .axis.zero), 100% at y=20 (inverse-scaled: higher
           progress = smaller y). Gridlines already placed below at 25/50/75/100%.
         1) IST (actual): replace the empty <path class="proj-line"> with its "d" attribute
            drawn through trajektorie.history[] points in order; repeat the <circle
            class="hist-pt"> template once per history point (loop var point., already
            wrapped below) with cx/cy computed from point.date_de/point.overall_progress_pct
