         2) IDEAL (reference): replace the empty <line class="ideal-line"> with x1/y1/x2/y2
            from (x(trajektorie.ideal.start_date_de), y=200) to
            (x(trajektorie.ideal.target_date_de), y=20), and position the "Ideal"
            <text class="ideal-label"> near its right end.
         Then place, using the same x mapping:
           - a <line class="marker-line"> + <text class="marker-label"> "HEUTE" at
             x(meta.report_date_de)
           - a <line class="marker-line"> + <text class="marker-label">
             "ZIELTERMIN {{trajektorie.target_date_de}}" at x(trajektorie.target_date_de)
           - IF trajektorie.stretch_date_de: a <line class="marker-line stretch"> + <text
             class="marker-label" style="fill:var(--tl-gelbrot)">
             "STRECKUNGSENDE {{trajektorie.stretch_date_de}}" at x(trajektorie.stretch_date_de)
         All rendered date labels use the _de (dd.mm.yyyy) fields verbatim — never render a
         raw ISO date token. -->
